43
00:02:29,080 --> 00:02:31,992
Would you tell the family
he's got a shot in hell?

44
00:02:32,160 --> 00:02:35,277
- Point taken.
- We have to try in vitro.

45
00:02:35,440 --> 00:02:37,908
