46
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:41,197
- Who is Peggy Woodruff?
- I met her in the elevator.

47
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:44,113
A lot of couples have trouble
conceiving.

48
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:46,794
